I was introduced to Chelsea wellness by a member of my family. First Impression  clean and welcoming. Friendly staff. It is one of one best foot massages I have  ever had. Eisen was extremely thorough with my requirements. I have a knee problem and Eisen worked on my knee ensuring by the end of my session it made a huge difference. I now feel light on my feet and can feel the difference after the foot massage.unreservedly I recommend to add Chelsea wellness to your itinerary list if visiting  Manhattan New York. Thank you all at Chelsea Wellness for helping me feel good.
Harshad London England.

originalText.text:
ℹ️Detailed Review - 60 Minute Couples Massage

Listen, I will say that if you are super melancholy and particular with massages, I don’t recommend that you go. The hassle of trying to nitpick their services of what you want/not want doesn’t seem worth the effort especially with the language barrier you may have.

If you do go, do communicate whether you want a man/woman to do the massage(if necessary). For me at least I’m more comfortable with a woman massaging me and luckily someone was there.

I almost booked through Groupon until I called and they mentioned $50/person (cash) My experience was great, I took my husband here for a couple’s massage for his birthday. We were both surprised with the “60 minute bodywork” as it is the WHOLE body. It was quiet, was a bit rough but tolerable for us. No actual complaints. They were nice and did their job. Just tip them. If you’re open to it, try them.

originalText.text:
First time coming here and I had a wonderful experience. The massage felt like a deep massage which at first hurt, but I think it was all tension. As the masseuse kept massaging me everything just felt amazing.

The woman was really attentive to every part of my body and couldn’t be more appreciative. I will definitely be coming back for another massage.

The facial was a bit different from what I’m used to. They didn’t steam my face or did any extractions.

originalText.text:
Last minute  find ! My friend had a birthday that just recently passed and we took a trip to New York.
I carefully read the prior views  and pictures and felt like this could be a trustworthy place and for a AMAZING PRICE!
I was able to get us both 45 min messages for about 109 and shared room. This place is beyond  clean.  When you first enter you are greeted and given a chance to look over what you would like and then walked us to the back.  Whats nice us that they will ask you before entering while are getting ready. They make sure to apply pressure when you ask to make sure you can relax.
I have since passed on this hidden gem to a ton of people  so it probably won't be hidden for long. Especially if they keep the prices the way they are. They can expect more people to come!
Must Check out! They excellent walk-ins and bookings. Very friendly location to come and relax a while.
